==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: homework
<hw>homework</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>preparatory school work
done outside school (especially at home).</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> prep, preparation.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <mark>[fig.]</mark> <def>Studies
or other preparatory work done prior to some activity; -- usually used
of preparations for activities of significance or consequence for the
performer; <as>as, the candidate didn't do her <ex>homework</ex> well
and was outclassed in the debate</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Paid work done at home, especially
piecework.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>homeworker</ent>⟦br⟧
